title: #133 - The Biggest Fail in YouTube History
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast Ethan, Hila, and the gang discuss a whole bevy of lighthearted stories... like the recent rash of mass shootings, blaming it on video games, Neil Degrasse Tyson being an idiot, Michael Avenatti blocking Ethan on twitter, and of course our main story- a YouTuber accidentally uploading a video of her hitting her dog! Have a great weekend everyone!
